      "1 ≤ **T** ≤ 50",
      "1 ≤ **n** ≤ 50",
      "1 ≤ **Ai** ≤ 109",
      "**A1** * **A2** * ... * **An** ≤ 109"
    ],
    "inputFormat": "**T****T****N****N****A1****A2****AN**",
    "outputFormat": "",
    "sampleTestCases": [
      {
        "id": "sample_1",
        "input": "3\n3\n1 3 2\n4\n4 1 2 1\n6\n1 2 2 2 2 1",
        "output": "4\n5\n9",
        "explanation": "Explanation:\nExample case 1. There are 4 such subarrays: A[1..1], A[2..2], A[3..3], A[1..3]. Consider A[1..3], sum = 1 + 3 + 2 = 6, product = 1 * 3 * 2 = 6."
